high_descs: turn around and walk forwards a bit, then hang a right and walk to the end of the room, then turn right to face the kitchen cabinets above
grab a cup out of the kitchen cabinet above
turn around and walk forwards a bit, and then down the room until you reach the fridge on the left
place the cup inside of the fridge, let it cool, then take it back out again
move to the end of the room on the left again, and turn right to face the black table at the end of the kitchen counters
place the cup down on the black table there
anns.task_desc: place a cooled cup down on the black table

high_descs: Turn left towards the black table at the corner and then look up at the cabinet above it.
Take out the cup from the cabinet.
Turn right and walk towards the fridge.
Place the cup on the top shelf inside the fridge, let it cool, and take it back out.
Turn left and head towards the small black table at the corner.
Place the cup at the right corner of the table.
anns.task_desc: Place a cooled cup on the black table.

high_descs: Turn around and take a step and then turn right and walk to the table then turn right.
Open the cabinet that's on the wall in front of you and get the coffee mug.
Turn around and take a step then turn left and walk to the fridge that will be on your left and stand in front of it facing it.
Put the mug on the top shelf of the fridge and close the door letting it cool off before retrieving it and closing the door again.
Walk back to where you got the mug from.
Put the mug in the bottom left corner of the small black table.
anns.task_desc: Put a cold mug on a black table.
